spec_data.Name: perl-Number-Range
spec_data.Description:
Number::Range will take a description of a range, and then allow you to test on
if a number falls within the range. You can also add and delete from the range.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:33:55 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Extension to work with ranges of numbers
